        protected void _exportToWebTest(java.lang.String modelFileName,
                                java.lang.String directoryName)
                         throws java.lang.Exception
        Test the ExportToWeb facility by reading in a model, and exporting it.

        This is the main entry point for ExportToWeb tests.

        The caller of this method need notbe in the Swing Event Thread.

        Parameters:
        modelFileName - The file name of the test model.
        directoryName - The name of the directory.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - If the file name cannot be read or exported
